RT @GavinNewsom  NEW: #CA is expanding eligibility for the #COVID19 #vaccine.
Beginning Apr 1, Californians 50+ will be able to sign up for an appt.
Beginning Apr 15, eligibility will be expanded to everyone 16 and older.
Light at the end of the tunnel continues to get brighter https://t.co/Ozw9lsQntW
